Data Manager - Project Road Map

The project plan consists of 2 major functional groups consisting of a number of component features:
  * Client-Side
    - Application initialization
    - App boot
    - Template designer
    - Data retrieval
    - Data insert/update/delete
    - Data synchronization
  * Server-Side
    - Database initialization
    - Data retrieval
    - Data insert/update/delete
    - Data synchronization
  
Each of these functional groups can be developed independently to some extent 
